quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,189,"Iye ndiye amene adakulengani inu kuchokera kwa munthu mmodzi ndipo kuchokera kwa munthu ameneyu adamulengera mkazi wake, kuti akhoza kupeza chisangalalo pokhala naye. Ndipo pamene iye amagona naye, iye adatenga pakati pamene ananyamula mosavutika. Koma pamene panakula, onse awiri amapempha Ambuye wawo: “Ngati Inu mutatipatsa mwana wabwino ndithudi ife tidzakhala othokoza.”"
  7,190,"Koma pamene akawapatsa mwana wabwino, iwo amakhazikitsa milungu ina pambali pa Iye kuthokoza pa zimene wawapatsa. Alemekezeke Mulungu kuposa zimene akumphatikiza nazo"
  7,191,Kodi iwo akukhazikitsa milungu ina pambali pa Mulungu weni weni imene siingathe kulenga zina zilizonse koma kuti nayonso ndi yolengedwa
  7,192,Palibe chimene ingawathandize ayi ndiponso iyo siingathe kudzithandiza yokha
  7,193,Ndipo ngati iwe uwaitana kunjira yoyenera iwo sadzakutsatira ayi. Ndi chimodzimodzi kwa iwe kaya uwaitana kapena ukhala chete
  7,194,Ndithudi iwo amene mumawapembedza powonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni ndi akapolo ngati inu nomwe. Motero aitaneni ndipo akuyankheni ngati zimene munena ndi zoonadi
  7,195,"Kodi iwo ali ndi miyendo yoti angayendere? Kodi ali ndi manja oti angagwire china chilichonse? Kapena ali ndi maso oti angaonere? Kapena ali ndi makutu oti angamvere? Nena, “Itanani milungu yanu yabodza ndipo pangani chiwembu chanu pa ine ndipo musandipatse mpumulo ayi.”"
  7,196,Ndithudi Mtetezi wanga ndi Mulungu amene wavumbulutsa Buku ndipo Iye ndi Mtetezi wa anthu a chilungamo
  7,197,Ndipo iwo amene mumawapembedza powonjezera pa Iye sangathe kukuthandizani inu ndiponso sangathe kudzithandiza iwo eni
  7,198,"Ndipo ngati iwe uwaitanira ku njira yoyenera, sakumva ayi ndipo udzawaona ali kukuyang’ana iwe koma sakuona ai"
  7,199,"Onetsa kukhululukira, lamulira zabwino ndipo uwapewe anthu osadziwa"
  7,200,"Ndipo ngati Satana akuyesa iwe, thawira kwa Mulungu. Ndithudi Iye ndi wakumva ndi wodziwa"
  7,201,"Ndithudi iwo amene amaopa Mulungu, ngati maganizo oipa adza kwa iwo kuchokera kwa Satana, iwo amakumbukira ndipo amaona kuunika"
  7,202,"Koma abale awo, iwo amawalowetsa mu uchimo ndipo salekerera"
  7,203,"Ndipo ngati iwe siubweretsa chozizwitsa iwo amati, “Kodi ndi chifukwa chiani siunabweretse?” Nena, “Ine ndimatsatira chokhacho chimene chavumbulutsidwa kwa ine kuchokera kwa Ambuye wanga.” Uwu ndi umboni wochokera kwa Ambuye wanu, malangizo ndi madalitso kwa anthu okhulupirira"
  7,204,"Ndipo pamene Korani ilakatulidwa, mverani ndipo khalani chete kuti mulandire madalitso"
  7,205,"Ndipo kumbukira Ambuye wako ndi lilime lako, mwa iwe wekha, modzichepetsa ndi mwamantha ndiponso mosakweza mawu m’mawa ndi masana ndipo usakhale ngati iwo a unyizi"
  7,206,Ndithudi iwo amene ali ndi Ambuye wako sanyada pogwira ntchito yopembedza Mulungu koma amamulemekeza Iye ndipo amagunditsa phumi zawo pamaso pake